summary:
Introducing the F You Sword. The F You Sword is a new retextured iron sword located in dragonsreach, on the wizard's table. The sword is ridiculously fast and has a base damage of 30.
Please don't take this mod seriously, i just made it in like 10 minutes becouse i was bored..
